    title: 'Employee Theft Prevention: What Your PoS Data Reveals About Internal Shrinkage',
    metaDescription: 'Internal theft costs small businesses billions annually. Learn how PoS void analysis, discount tracking, and drawer reports expose employee theft patterns before losses mount.',
