    title: 'Mobile Payment Reconciliation for Food Trucks: One Dashboard for Cash, Card, and Wallet',
    metaDescription: 'Food trucks juggle cash, card readers, and mobile wallets with no back office. Learn how unified PoS reconciliation prevents revenue from falling through the cracks.',
